<p>I had great luck as today 
<lb/> was a glorious day and yet 
<lb/> not too hot for marching 
<lb/> (here is about 8 miles from 
<lb/> Lenan to railway station 
<lb/> Clonmany) I arrived at 
<lb/> Grey Pt. about 7.30 just in 
