<lb/>with him &#x2014; we missed the 
<lb/>train so he motored me 
<lb/>in &#x2014; a very nice little 
<lb/>run &#x2014; I am very 
<lb/>delighted to have left the 
<lb/>Swilly behind if only for 
<lb/>the day and I haven't 
<lb/>to return till Wednesday.
<lb/>It's a pity I don't know 
<lb/>anyone in Belfast.</p>
<p>Please thank Win for her 
<lb/>letter. Its grand the <unclear>wives</unclear> 
